    "description": "Police Shootout: Prologue是一款回合制第一人称射击游戏。开始一名警察的职业生涯，破获案件、获取工作经验，即刻投身到在圣阿德里诺的冒险生活吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661280/extras/c5890517ab909ace9fa6290a9235f94f.avif?t=1743592223\" width=610 height=343 /></span><br><br><strong>欢迎来到圣阿德里诺</strong><br>你的名字叫斯科特·普赖斯，你刚开始在圣阿德里诺这个小城作为警察第一次当班。你是从一个比这里大得多的城市搬来这里的，在那里的街头，处理帮派斗殴可谓是一种工作常态。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661280/extras/008309bcd55d975b7bc0ddc8086ae973.poster.avif?t=1743592223\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661280/extras/008309bcd55d975b7bc0ddc8086ae973.webm?t=1743592223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661280/extras/008309bcd55d975b7bc0ddc8086ae973.mp4?t=1743592223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>那我来问问你......</strong><br>为什么像你这样的警察 - 在大城市做得很好的人突然要冒险来这种地方工作？你是来这里寻找什么吗？有什么其他理由吗？又或是......你有什么不可告人的秘密？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661280/extras/a0e3e87058a94fdb0c825acd0e393a54.poster.avif?t=1743592223\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661280/extras/a0e3e87058a94fdb0c825acd0e393a54.webm?t=1743592223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661280/extras/a0e3e87058a94fdb0c825acd0e393a54.mp4?t=1743592223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>咱们说说这个游戏......</strong><br>Police Shootout将带你开始你的冒险生活，你不仅要作为主角（斯科特·普赖斯）行事，还要面对在他的故事中各个重要的角色。作为一名尽职的警官，你将要处理极为棘手的案件。有人抢劫商店，还绑架了人质 - 你必须筹划好一切！但请记住 - 如何处理具体的情况需要你自己拿主意。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661280/extras/885aea9f7c0e7b73d9bfbce056b296b6.poster.avif?t=1743592223\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661280/extras/885aea9f7c0e7b73d9bfbce056b296b6.webm?t=1743592223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661280/extras/885aea9f7c0e7b73d9bfbce056b296b6.mp4?t=1743592223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>你终将成为一名怎样的警察？你的破案风格会怎样？</strong><br>要做好这些事取决于许多因素 - 有时需要直接用枪，而有时强有力的论点论据亦可做为最具杀伤力的武器使用。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661280/extras/8d10b3e7b7c8f5c4db08a5c4c4fadfd5.poster.avif?t=1743592223\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661280/extras/8d10b3e7b7c8f5c4db08a5c4c4fadfd5.webm?t=1743592223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661280/extras/8d10b3e7b7c8f5c4db08a5c4c4fadfd5.mp4?t=1743592223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>每种情况都使你更接近于找到你所要寻找的东西...... 当然也是为了成为一名更好的警察而努力! 正确处理案件的方式将有效提升你的工作经验 - 它越高，就越会有更多的好处给你。你的技能将取决于你想如何让它增长，这能让你更快、更高效地完成新任务。<br><br><strong>我们开始工作吧!</strong><br>你准备好介入并把案件顺利解决了吗？没什么可等的，第一个案子正等着你来处理呢!<br><br>不如进入游戏赶快行动起来吧!",
